paragraphs.text:
run("
SELECT *
FROM(
    SELECT distinct substr(orderDate, 6,2) as month
            ,SUM(NMIncAd)/COUNT(DISTINCT atb.subOrderId) AS NMBO
            ,count(distinct f.fto) as ftu_orders
    FROM(
    select orderId as fto from `temp.ftu___3` 
        ) f
    
    LEFT JOIN(
    SELECT *       
        FROM `temp.order_sd`
        WHERE orderDate>='2022-10-01'
    )atb
    on atb.orderId=f.fto
    
    LEFT JOIN(
            SELECT DISTINCT subOrderId
                            ,NMIncAd
            FROM `all(unitEconomicsBaseTable)`
            ) ue
    ON atb.subOrderId = ue.subOrderId
    
    GROUP BY substr(orderDate, 6,2)
    ORDER BY month
    )
",1000)
